org.rocketproplab.marginalstability.flightcomputer.hal

Interface IMU

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    LSM9DS1

    public interface IMU
    An interface for an Inertial Measurement Unit. An IMU implementing this interface will give an iterable list of IMUReadings. If hasNext returns true there will be at least another IMU Reading.
    Author:
    max

    • Method Summary
